---
title: Herby Pork Cotoletta Panini with Garlic Potatoes & Mayonnaise
description: This dish is full of tantalizing flavours, from the garlic butter drizzled over the potatoes to the herby Tuscan seasoning cooked
right into the pork crumb. Even the panini is getting a boost with a swipe of mayonnaise to tie it all together!
